# android_v1_scope.me
# Purpose: Defines the exact feature scope for Android v1. Explicitly lists what
#          is included, what is excluded, feature priority, dependencies, and
#          blockers that must be resolved before implementation can begin.
# Scope: Android v1 only. Does not define iOS behaviour or backend changes.

---

## SCOPE PRINCIPLE

Android v1 is a **player-facing app**. It covers everything a player needs to
discover, book, attend, and pay for pickleball games. Club owner and admin tools
are out of scope for v1 with specific exceptions noted below.

Backend is shared with iOS. No new Supabase tables, RPCs, or Edge Functions are
required for Android v1, with two exceptions noted in §4.

---

## 1. IN SCOPE — INCLUDED FEATURES

### Authentication
- Email + password sign up and sign in
- Session persistence (auto re-auth on app launch)
- Sign out
- Auth state bootstrap guard (see `client_guardrails.me §7`)

### Profile
- View own profile (name, email, phone, skill level, DUPR rating)
- Edit and save profile
- Avatar display (preset selection — not upload in v1)
- DUPR rating display (from Supabase + local cache)
- DUPR rating sync from backend after every profile fetch

### Club Discovery
- Browse clubs list (all clubs)
- Nearby clubs (location-based, sorted by distance)
- Club detail view:
  - Info tab (name, address, description, membership status)
  - Games tab (upcoming games for that club)
  - Members tab (club member list)
  - Club Chat tab (see Club Chat below)
- Join / leave club (membership request and approval flow)
- Pull-to-refresh on all club lists

### Game Discovery
- Upcoming games feed (cross-club)
- Nearby games (location-based)
- Game detail view (full info, attendee list, booking CTA)
- Filter by skill level
- Scheduled/unpublished games: hidden from player view entirely

### Booking — Free Games
- Book a free game
- Cancel a confirmed booking (no credit window — free)
- View booking confirmation state
- Waitlist join for full free games
- Automatic waitlist promotion for free games (multi-promote)

### Booking — Paid Games
- Book a paid game via Stripe PaymentSheet (card + Google Pay)
- Credit application at checkout (toggle, net price display)
- Full credit cover path (skip Stripe, deduct credits only)
- Cancel a paid booking:
  - Within 6h of game: no credit
  - Outside 6h: credit issued to club-scoped balance
- Cancellation credit feedback (amount credited, new balance)
- `pending_payment` state display with live countdown
- "Complete Booking" CTA for promoted waitlist players
- "Spot hold expired" passive state + Refresh

### Credits
- View credit balance per club (on club detail and booking screen)
- View credit balance pills on bookings list (one per club with positive balance)
- Apply credits at checkout (partial and full cover)
- Balance refresh after cancellation, booking, and on view load
- All operations are club-scoped (see `system_contracts.me §3`)

### Notifications
- Push notifications via FCM (see `platform_adaptation.me §3`)
- In-app notifications list
- Mark as read
- Clear all
- Notification tap routing:
  - Club → club detail inline navigation
  - Game → game detail modal
  - Review prompt → review sheet modal
- Notification types: booking_confirmed, game_cancelled, waitlist_promoted,
  club_announcement, club_chat_mention, club_chat_reply, game_review_request

### Bookings List
- View all upcoming and past bookings
- Booking state displayed per item (confirmed, waitlisted, pending_payment, cancelled)
- Cancel booking from list
- Credit balance pills per club

### Club Chat
- View club news / chat feed
- Post a text message (player post, not announcement)
- Comment on a post
- Like a post
- View images in posts (display only — no upload in v1)
- Mentions (@username) — display only; mention notifications received
- Real-time or pull-to-refresh updates

### Reviews
- Receive review prompt notification 24h after game ends
- Submit a star rating (1–5) + optional comment via review sheet
- View reviews section on club detail (aggregate stars, individual reviews)
- Duplicate review handling: "You have already left a review for this session."

### Deep Links
- Handle `bookadink://club/{id}` → open club detail
- Handle `bookadink://game/{id}` → open game detail
- Handle `bookadink://booking/{id}` → open booking detail
- Handle `bookadink://review/{gameID}` → no-op (review comes via notification only)

