## 2. OUT OF SCOPE — EXCLUDED FROM ANDROID V1

These features exist on iOS but are NOT included in Android v1.

### Club Owner and Admin Tools (entire category)
- Club creation
- Club editing (name, description, address, image, settings)
- Club analytics dashboard
- Game creation and editing
- Manage games modal (admin game cards, fill status, cancellations)
- Add player to game (admin)
- Attendance tracking and check-in
- Join request approval / rejection
- Manage members (promote, remove)
- Club subscription management UI
- Stripe Connect onboarding
- "Delayed publish" (publish_at) game scheduling UI
- Club announcement posts (admin-only post type)
- Announcement mode toggle in club chat composer

### Profile Features
- DUPR rating history chart (`DUPRHistoryCard`)
- Custom avatar upload (view preset only)
- Badges card

### Payment Features
- Stripe Connect onboarding for club owners
- Subscription upgrade / downgrade UI
- Billing portal

### Media
- Image upload (club banners, club avatars, chat images)
- Splash screen video (use static splash)

### Content
- Pickleball news feed (The Dink RSS — deferred to v1.x)

### Misc
- "Win Rate" stat — no data backing; never implement on any platform

