## 3. FEATURE PRIORITY AND DEPENDENCY MAP

Priority order for implementation. Each feature depends on those above it.

```
P0 — FOUNDATION (must ship before anything else)
├── Auth (sign up, sign in, session persistence)
├── Profile (view + edit)
└── Supabase client setup + token injection

P1 — DISCOVERY (required before booking)
├── Club list + Club detail
├── Game list + Game detail
└── Nearby games + clubs (location permission)

P2 — BOOKING — FREE (core player value)
├── Book a free game
├── Cancel a booking
├── Waitlist join
└── Auto-promote waitlist (free games)

P3 — BOOKING — PAID (requires P2 complete + Stripe SDK wired)
├── Stripe PaymentSheet integration
├── Book a paid game (card + Google Pay)
├── pending_payment state + hold countdown
└── Complete booking (waitlist hold path)

P4 — CREDITS (requires P3 complete)
├── Credit balance fetch (club-scoped)
├── Apply credits at checkout
├── Cancellation credit issuance
└── Credit display (club detail, bookings list, checkout)

P5 — NOTIFICATIONS (can develop in parallel with P3/P4)
├── FCM token registration
├── In-app notification list
├── Notification tap routing
└── Clear all

P6 — CLUB CHAT (requires P1 complete)
├── Feed view (posts, comments, likes)
├── Post + comment composer
└── Mention display

P7 — REVIEWS (requires P5 complete)
├── Review sheet (submit rating + comment)
├── Reviews section on club detail
└── Duplicate review handling
```

